The eco-friendly alternative 

The city of Vancouver has banned plastic straws and it's time for all of us to start moving away from the use of single-use plastic. Here are 7 eco-friendly alternatives to the plastic straw. Why? Because #strawssuck.
https://www.globalcitizen.org/en/content/alternatives-to-plastic-straws-eco-friendly/

